* version 3.0.0 (###)

Added full Unicode support.

* version 3.1.0 (###)

Added the @mzero, @mcopy, @malloc, and @mfree opcodes.

* version 3.1.1 (###)

Added the acceleration opcodes.

* version 3.1.2 (August 18, 2010)

Added floating-point opcodes.
Deprecated 8-bit and 16-bit locals.
More accelerated functions (late update: March 27, 2014)

* version 3.1.3 (###)

Added the @hasundo and @discardundo opcodes.
